fastx_spats_toolkit_0.0.1 is a modified version of fastx toolkit Based off of version 0.0.13.2 from http://hannonlab.cshl.edu/fastx_toolkit/download.html.
Modifications include adjustments to fastx_clipper to allow stringent (no mismatch) matching of adapters.

Before installing spats, copy the entire directory to the build directory and go through the normal fastx installation.

Spats v1.0.1 - Only fastx_revcomp is required


